## Purpose of Function:                                                             #
##  HTTP-triggered Azure Function that exposes ONE endpoint with TWO modes,         #
##  selected by the 'agent' field in the request:                                   #
##                                                                                  #
##    agent = 'detect'    -> returns ONLY the detected language of 'message'        #
##                           [offline, deterministic, no LLM].                      #
##    agent = 'translate' -> translates 'message' into the target 'lang' using      #
##                           the Azure AI Foundry 'multilingual-agent'.             #
##                                                                                  #
## IMPORTANT (auth): the Foundry 'projects' endpoint uses Microsoft Entra ID only. #
## The Function App's Managed Identity MUST live in the SAME tenant as the Foundry  #
## project (e.g. Teva) and be granted the 'Azure AI User' role on that project.     #
## A managed identity cannot authenticate across tenants, and API keys do NOT work  #
## for this endpoint.                                                               #
